    "attributes": {
        "action": "Remove guidance on schools telling parents about gender questioning children",
        "additional_details": "It could also limit social transition which could exacerbate or cause mental health issues. We think that if schools and colleges follow this guidance, it would cause a lot of harm.",
        "background": "The draft guidance would mean that schools have to tell parents, except in rare circumstances, about children's gender identity, which could put them in danger. ",
